ns0:value.ns0:const: To confirm DID ranges between EDA0 - EDFF returns ECU Identifcation and Configuration Records. Verify by reading the Composite DID 0xEDA0 in Boot Mode.
DID EDA0 Complete ECU Part/Serial Number(s) Read
1. In SPA2 DSA, set ECU to 1D7D and read the DID 0xED A0 (0x721 03 22 ED A0) and verify the response.

1. Verify the response 0x62 ED A0 and it shall contain below ECU Identification records. DID 0xF121 Primary Bootloader Diagnostic Database Part Number DID 0xF12A ECU Core Assembly Part Number DID 0xF12B ECU Delivery Assembly Part Number DID 0xF18C ECU Serial Number DID 0xF125 Primary Bootloader Software Part Number
To confirm Primary Bootloader Software Part Number by reading the DID 0xF125 in PBL mode.
DID F125 Primary Bootloader Software Part Number Read
1. Open DSA tool and send DIAG command 0x10 02 to enter to Boot Mode. (0x721 02 10 02). 2. Read the Primary Bootloader Software Part Number by sending the DIAG command 0x22 F1 25 (0x721 03 22 F1 25)

1. Verify Positive Response for Session Control Request (0x621 50 01) 2. Verify the Positive Response and Part Number as per the Software Flashed. (0x621 62 F1 25 XX XX XX XX XX XX XX ) - XX need to be compared with the Part Number sheet for the respective release.
To confirm Primary Bootloader Software Part Number by reading the DID 0xF125 in SBL Boot mode.
DID F125 Primary Bootloader Software Part Number Read
1. Open DSA tool and send DIAG command 0x10 02 to enter to Boot Mode. (0x721 02 10 02). 2. Read the Primary Bootloader Software Part Number by sending the DIAG command 0x22 F1 25 (0x721 03 22 F1 25)

1. Verify Positive Response for Session Control Request (0x621 50 02) 2. Verify the Positive Response and Part Number as per the Software Flashed. (0x621 62 F1 25 XX XX XX XX XX XX XX ) - XX need to be compared with the Part Number sheet for the respective release.
To confirm ECU Software Part Number data record by reading the DID 0xF12E in Default Session.
DID F12E ECU Software Part Numbers Read

1. Open DSA tool and send DIAG command 0x10 01 to enter to Default Session. (0x721 02 10 01). 2. Read the ECU Software Part Number data record by sending the DIAG command 0x22 F1 2E (0x721 03 22 F1 2E)

1. Verify Positive Response for Session Control Request (0x621 50 01) 2. Verify the Positive Response and ECU Software Part Number data record as per the Software Flashed. (0x621 62 F1 2E XX XX XX XX XX XX XX ) - XX need to be compared with the Part Number sheet for the respective release.
To confirm ECU Software Part Number data record by reading the DID 0xF12E in Default Session.
DID F12E ECU Software Part Numbers Read

1. Open DSA tool and send DIAG command 0x10 03 to enter to Extended Session. (0x721 02 10 01). 2. Read the ECU Software Part Number data record by sending the DIAG command 0x22 F1 2E (0x721 03 22 F1 2E)

1. Verify Positive Response for Session Control Request (0x621 50 01) 2. Verify the Positive Response and ECU Software Part Number data record as per the Software Flashed. (0x621 62 F1 2E XX XX XX XX XX XX XX ) - XX need to be compared with the Part Number sheet for the respective release.
